Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:08.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:09.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}近づいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}真っ白な世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:18.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}たった一つだけの約束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:30.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}きっと忘れないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:34.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}二人過ごした永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:37.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}照れ臭そうに手招く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:41.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}無邪気な時の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:44.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}言葉で伝えるには
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}未完成な感情です
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}運命を嘆くほど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:56.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}私たち弱くはない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:59.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}ねぇそうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:01.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:03.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}動き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:06.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}選び取る答えに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:10.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}心ちぎれそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:14.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}守りたいものがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:18.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}ためらいの朝　迷いの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:21.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}もし手を離しても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:27.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}必ずたどり着くと信じてます
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.61,0:24:33.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}私を呼ぶ声が聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.05,0:25:24.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}素直じゃない態度にも
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:28.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}優しさを見せる人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:31.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}ぬくもりに触れるたび
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.91,0:25:36.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}私は私になれた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.06,0:25:38.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}ひだまりを追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.92,0:25:43.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}満ちる花びらみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.47,0:25:46.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}溢れてしまう気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.24,0:25:50.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}切なさに立ち尽くすのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.71,0:25:53.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}ねぇどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:55.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}なんにも見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.14,0:25:57.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}音の消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.93,0:26:00.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}静寂の彼方で
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:05.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}与えられた使命を
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.38,0:26:08.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}超えてゆく確かな決意
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.96,0:26:10.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}戦いの後
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.94,0:26:12.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}冷めない熱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:15.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}幾度も襲っても
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.68,0:26:22.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}一緒ならば　行けるはず未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.98,0:26:33.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}眩しい希望　貴方ごと全部
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.52,0:26:36.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}私にください
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.46,0:26:42.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}近づいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.30,0:26:45.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}懐かしい響きに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.52,0:26:49.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}導かれるみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.62,0:26:53.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}私もそこへ向かってく
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.38,0:26:57.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}ためらいの朝　迷いの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.08,0:26:59.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}もし手を離しても
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.02,0:27:06.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}必ずたどり着くと信じてます
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.36,0:27:12.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}受け取った約束があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:08.11,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}在某處呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:09.86,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}離我近點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.87,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}在純白的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:18.29,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}只有一個承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:30.22,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}我相信你不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:34.10,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}我們一起度過的永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:37.60,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}你的招呼讓我害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:41.69,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}在純真的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:44.52,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}要我用言語說明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:48.57,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}是一種不完整的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.91,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}命運的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:56.37,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}我們的關係會更脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:59.16,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}嘿，對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:01.58,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}在某處呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:03.46,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}快點來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:06.38,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}我不知道怎麼回答
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:10.76,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}即使我放下我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:14.51,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}因為有想要守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:18.18,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}早上的混亂，晚上的猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:21.23,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}就算放開你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:27.69,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}我相信你會到達那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.61,0:24:33.86,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}你能聽見我的心聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.05,0:25:24.55,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}即使你不誠實
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:28.47,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}因為被甜言蜜語吞食
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:31.90,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}每次我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.91,0:25:36.05,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}我變成了真實的我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.06,0:25:38.91,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}像追逐陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.92,0:25:43.02,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}我的道路被花瓣裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.47,0:25:46.23,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}滿溢的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.24,0:25:50.70,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}我會忍受難過
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.71,0:25:53.48,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}嘿，為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:55.92,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\an9}什麼都看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.14,0:25:57.92,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&\}聲音消散
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.93,0:26:00.33,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}遠方静寂
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:05.30,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}賦予的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.38,0:26:08.82,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}克服困難的堅定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.96,0:26:10.88,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}戰爭結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.94,0:26:12.62,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}永不冷卻的熱度
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:15.58,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}不管我襲擊多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.68,0:26:22.94,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}如果在一起 為了到達幸福的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.98,0:26:33.44,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}令人眼花繚亂的希望，我傾盡所有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.52,0:26:36.88,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.36,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在某處呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.46,0:26:42.16,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}離我近點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.30,0:26:45.14,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}想念他的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.52,0:26:49.50,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}彷彿被引導
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.62,0:26:53.30,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}告訴我方向
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.38,0:26:57.00,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}早上的混亂，晚上的猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.08,0:26:59.84,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}就算放開你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.02,0:27:06.52,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我相信你會到達那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.36,0:27:12.84,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}因為我收到的承諾
